cssFile: home
tags:
  - projects
section: themes
order: 3
featured: true
projectId: kenny.cx
projectUrl: https://www.kenny.cx
imageAlt: kenny.cx personal site screenshot
description: kenny.cx is my personal portfolio site, built to highlight the creative and technical work I have done over the years, from custom themes and tools to experiments that started as simple ideas and grew into something worth sharing.
summary: My personal portfolio site, built with 11ty.
---

<section class="py-md-6 py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row mb-3">
            <div class="col">
                <p class="lead fw-normal">{{ description }}</p>
                <p><a href="{{ projectUrl }}" class="link-stckr">{{ projectUrl }}</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-4 g-md-5 mb-4">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-4">
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <div class="text-stckr me-4">
                        {% include "svg/11ty.njk" %}
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h5 class="mb-2 mb-lg-3 fw-bold">Why 11ty?</h5>
                        <p>I chose Eleventy (11ty) because it’s fast, flexible, and lets me build exactly the kind of site I want—without getting in my way. Its simplicity and power make it perfect for a creative portfolio.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-4">
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <div class="text-stckr me-4">
                        {% include "svg/bootstrap.njk" %}
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h5 class="mb-2 mb-lg-3 fw-bold">Why Bootstrap?</h5>
                        <p>I use Bootstrap because it gives me a solid, responsive grid and a ton of utility classes—so I can focus on design and content, not reinventing the basics.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-4">
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <div class="text-stckr me-4">
                        {% include "svg/nunjucks.njk" %}
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h5 class="mb-2 mb-lg-3 fw-bold">Why Nunjucks?</h5>
                        <p>Nunjucks lets me write templates that are clean, readable, and reusable. It’s powerful enough for complex layouts, but simple enough to keep everything maintainable.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mb-4">
            {% set heroImage = projectId | assetImagePath('png', '', tags, 'lg') %}
            <img src="{{ heroImage | url }}" class="card-img h-100"
                alt="{{ imageAlt or (title ~ ' screenshot') }}">
        </div>
        <p><a href="{{ '/projects' | url }}" class="btn btn-outline-stckr btn-sm">Back to all projects</a></p>
    </div>
</section>